// Envelope: { sessionId, userId, userName?, message? | chatInput? }
// Antepõe [CONTEXTO DO USUÁRIO ...]; o trigger da tabela nl_chat_message lê
// esse bloco para popular user_id.
const body = $input.first().json.body ?? $input.first().json;
const sessionId = (body.sessionId || '').toString().trim();
const userId    = (body.userId    || '').toString().trim();
const userName  = (body.userName  || '').toString().trim();
let rawMsg      = (body.message   || body.chatInput || '').toString();
rawMsg = rawMsg.replace(/^\s*\[CONTEXTO[^\]]*\]\s*/i, '').trim();
if (!sessionId) throw new Error('sessionId is required');
if (!userId)    throw new Error('userId is required');
const header = `[CONTEXTO DO USUÁRIO: nome="${userName}" ID="${userId}"]`;
const chatInput = `${header}\n\n${rawMsg}`;
return { sessionId, userId, userName, chatInput, original_message: rawMsg };
